```sql

SELECT 
    p.EmployeeNumber, 
    p.Age, 
    p.Gender, 
    a.Attrition, 
    a.Department
FROM 
    hr_personal_data AS p
LEFT JOIN 
    hr_attrition_data AS a
ON 
    p.EmployeeNumber = a.EmployeeNumber
ORDER BY 
    p.EmployeeNumber ASC;

    p.EmployeeNumber, 
    p.Age, 
    p.Gender,

    hr_personal_data AS p

    hr_attrition_data AS a
ON 
    p.EmployeeNumber = a.EmployeeNumber
ORDER BY 
    p.EmployeeNumber ASC;

    p.EmployeeNumber, 
    p.Age, 
    p.Gender, 
    a.Attrition, 
    a.Department
FROM 
    hr_personal_data AS p
LEFT JOIN 
    hr_attrition_data AS a
ON 
    p.EmployeeNumber = a.EmployeeNumber
ORDER BY 
    p.EmployeeNumber ASC;

    p.EmployeeNumber, 
    p.Age, 
    p.Gender, 
    a.Attrition, 
    a.Department
FROM 
    hr_personal_data AS p
LEFT JOIN 
    hr_attrition_data AS a
ON 
    p.EmployeeNumber = a.EmployeeNumber
ORDER BY 
    p.EmployeeNumber ASC;

    p.EmployeeNumber, 
    p.Age, 
    p.Gender,

    a.Department

    hr_personal_data AS p
LEFT JOIN 
    hr_attrition_data AS a
ON 
    p.EmployeeNumber = a.EmployeeNumber
ORDER BY 
    p.EmployeeNumber ASC;

    hr_attrition_data AS a
ON 
    p.EmployeeNumber = a.EmployeeNumber
ORDER BY 
    p.EmployeeNumber ASC;

    p.EmployeeNumber, 
    p.Age, 
    p.Gender, 
    a.Attrition, 
    a.Department

    hr_personal_data AS p
LEFT JOIN 
    hr_attrition_data AS a
ON 
    p.EmployeeNumber = a.EmployeeNumber
ORDER BY 
    p.EmployeeNumber ASC;

    p.EmployeeNumber, 
    p.Age, 
    p.Gender, 
    a.Attrition, 
    a.Department
FROM 
    hr_personal_data AS p
LEFT JOIN 
    hr_attrition_data AS a
ON 
    p.EmployeeNumber = a.EmployeeNumber
ORDER BY 
    p.EmployeeNumber ASC;

    p.EmployeeNumber, 
    p.Age, 
    p.Gender, 
    a.Attrition, 
    a.Department

    hr_personal_data AS p
LEFT JOIN 
    hr_attrition_data AS a
ON 
    p.EmployeeNumber = a.EmployeeNumber
ORDER BY 
    p.EmployeeNumber ASC;

    p.EmployeeNumber,

    hr_personal_data AS p

    hr_attrition_data AS a
ON 
    p.EmployeeNumber = a.EmployeeNumber
ORDER BY 
    p.EmployeeNumber ASC;

    hr_attrition_data AS a
ON 
    p.EmployeeNumber = a.EmployeeNumber
ORDER BY 
    p.EmployeeNumber ASC;

ON 
    p.EmployeeNumber = a.EmployeeNumber
ORDER BY 
    p.EmployeeNumber ASC;
